<!DOCTYPE html>

<html style="height:100%;width:100%;margin:0px;">

<head>
	{{> head}}

	<title> WebExhibition - {{title}}</title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="./dist/css/game.css">
	<script type="text/javascript" src="https://unpkg.com/vue@2.1.6/dist/vue.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
	{{> header}}
	<header>
		{{> block-header}}
	</header>

	<nav>
		<h3>掌蚊宗師</h3>
	</nav>

	<section>
		<div class="section-title">
			<h1 class="col-xs-6 col-md-2 col-md-offset-1">目標問題</h1>
		</div>

		<div class="row">
			<div class="section-content col-xs-8 col-xs-offset-2 col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-3">
				<p>因應掌蚊人網站的誕生，因此陸續想到以遊戲的方式吸引兒童的客群，希望更能從小建立觀念，解決此環境病問題。</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="section-title">
			<h1 class="col-xs-6 col-md-2 col-md-offset-1">如何思考</h1>
		</div>

		<div class="row">
			<div class="section-content col-xs-8 col-xs-offset-2 col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-3">
				<ul>
					<li>定義此遊戲想透過<span class="color-blue">練武功吃卷軸打敗蚊子</span>的方式進行</li>

					<li>捲軸為「防蚊三招」，讓使用者反覆看到，潛移默化地接收</li>

					<li>主視覺： 綠色代表「環境」，黃色代表「溫暖」。
					</li>

					<li class="p-font-400 color-blue">好的遊戲，不應該具備複雜的操作和設定，要用簡單直覺的方式來破關</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="section-title">
			<h1 class="col-xs-6 col-md-2 col-md-offset-1">專案成果</h1>
		</div>

		<div class="row">
			<div class="section-board col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
				<div id="board-game" class="board-img" onclick="window.open('http://www.denguefever.tw/interact/game/Mosquito_war/');"></div>
				<div class="board-content">
					<h2>掌蚊宗師</h2>
					<p class="color-purple">一場對抗登革熱的修煉</p>
					<br>
					<div class="board-link">
						<a href="http://www.denguefever.tw/interact/game/Mosquito_war/" target="_blank">
							<i class="fa fa-eye" aria-hidden="true"></i>
						</a>
						<a href="https://github.com/TseHang/theMosquitoMan/tree/gh-pages/interact/game/Mosquito_war" target="_blank">
							<i class="fa fa-github" aria-hidden="true"></i>
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="circle"></div>
			</div>
		</div>

	</section>

	{{> gogoGuide}} {{> footer}}


</body>

{{> js-include}}
<script type="text/javascript" src="dist/js/block-game.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	$('.gogoGuide').addClass('hover');

	window.setTimeout(function () {
		$('.gogoGuide').removeClass('hover');
	}, 2000);
</script>

</html>